g flavors and smooth mouthfeel.  Fondant was dense and intensely chocolatey.  Pear clafoutis was brought hot from the oven.  The sweet pear made the dish too sweet.  A tart fruit like raspberries or cherries would have given the dish a better balance.  http://www.danielnyc.com/dbbrasserie/_pdf/menu.pdf

